title: Aerosmith Discography
description:
Here is the full discography for Aerosmith.  My idea of a full discography is all studio albums and compilation albums, and all soundtrack songs.  No bootlegs, etc. They are all MP3 VBR192.  They sound great. If you want better quality go elsewhere. Trolling will get you nowhere.  And they are FREE!  All nicely tagged, with artwork. That being said here is what you get:

Aerosmith
Get Your Wings
Toys In The Attic
Rocks
Draw The Line
Night In The Ruts
Rock In A Hard Place
Done With Mirrors
Permanent Vacation
Pump
Get A Grip
Nine Lives
Just Push Play
Honkin' A Bobo
Music From Another Dimension!

There is also a folder called other singles that have their soundtrack appearances in it which are:

Love Me Two Times - Air America Soundtrack
Deuces Are Wild - The Beavis and Butt-Head Experience
Angel's Eye - Charlie's Angels Soundtrack
I Don't Want To Miss A Thing - Armageddon Soundtrack
What Kind Of Love Are You On - Armageddon Soundtrack
Sweet Emotion - Armageddon Soundtrack
Come Together - Armageddon SOundtrack

So please enjoy, share and leave feedback!
